'''Keskmaa Ordu''' (abbr. KO), is a [[Tolkien Societies|Tolkien society]] in Estonia. As of 2024, the group is active on Facebook, and has hosted events as recently as 2023.<ref>[https://www.facebook.com/groups/326053679867/ Keskmaa Ordu Facebook], [https://www.facebook.com/groups/326053679867/events Events] (accessed 7 April 2024)</ref>
